　　　戯詠<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">二</seg>淡婆姑<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">一</seg>所管多植此<lb />
民間多種是耶非　穀外常偸田土肥　所<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>見眼前含<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>露秀　安知身後作<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>煙飛　余<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>茎長植吟翁杖　編<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>葉時懸羽客衣　租税頗憑<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">二</seg>婆子力<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">一</seg>　休<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>言此物不<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>充<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>饑<lb />
